{"tid":1304603,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"地政總署：大埔連儂隧道七月十二日要清場！！！","createTime":"2019-07-10T15:57:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T09:24:31.000Z","uid":28114,"like":13,"dislike":127,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"1c6218198623aeedaa50931e140d5c830a57f4da","tid":1304603,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:57:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10162400337920352&amp;set=gm.10162146907950245&amp;type=3&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D10162400337920352%26set%3Dgm.10162146907950245%26type%3D3%26sfns%3Dmo&d=RGEj3L6UPYZQbhamDwVV3b3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=c742c62e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10162400337920352&amp;set=gm.10162146907950245&amp;type=3&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n各位.<br />\n唔知大家黎左連儂隧道未呢？<br />\n不論你想黎向政府表達心聲、向同學表達支持、向市民表達關心定係表達不同的政治立場同意見<br />\n連儂隧道都比到呢個機會<br />\n大埔連儂隧道雖然只係短短幾日<br />\n但已經今大家we connect <br />\n除左大埔居民仲有全港十八區香港人黎到感受呢份大埔嘅愛同打令人起雞皮的震撼<br />\n但....今天在memo群中偷偷出現了一張地政總署的通知書<br />\n兩日後七月十二日連儂隧道即將面臨清場的命運<br />\n各位！ 政府清得走我們的memo <br />\n但清不走我們的聲音，清不走我們的信念！ <br />\n因為民主的信念不是活於memo內不僅存在於連儂隧道內！這是不局限於形式！<br />\n而是活於全部香港人的心內！<br />\n我們不知道那日連儂再會出現，但我相信大家意志不死的！<br />\n把握時間，讓沒來過的人來！<br />\n叫仍沉睡的人醒覺過來！<br />\n連儂隧道便完成了他的意義！ <br />\n來拍照把！來打咭吧！來看吧！來銘記於我們的心吧！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uNQXgtK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuNQXgtK.png&h=8ea4859c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0a7c105f321dfe6f4cd64b47d6665532f9ccd98a","tid":1304603,"uid":61520,"like":54,"dislike":4,"score":50,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:58:08.000Z","msg":"目前戰線太多，運動重心稍為偏離；大家花太多時間係寶礦力同連儂場上面。<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地需要集中火力係五大訴求上面。</span></span></strong>只有個議題仲係度，個運動先繼續有力量做其他野。重心要放返係「送中」上面，連帶反黑警；連儂場唔好太執著、反TVB唔好反多過林鄭。先搞「送中」，燈柱同信用評分先慢慢普及。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">重心一定要放返係「送中」上面！<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聚焦五大訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連儂牆由得佢，第日再整過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/2387482604810123/posts/2908010702757308?s=625469440&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=xmo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F2387482604810123%2Fposts%2F2908010702757308%3Fs%3D625469440%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dxmo&d=RGEj3L6UPYZQbhamDwVV3b3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=4f7169a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/2387482604810123/posts/2908010702757308?s=625469440&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=xmo</a>"},{"pid":"ba7316a5179f17dd48514090dae4010116b6afcd","tid":1304603,"uid":73826,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:59:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">重申抗爭所堅持之五大訴求:<br />\n一、撤回修例<br />\n二、撤回6.12暴動定性<br />\n三、撤銷反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、責成獨立調查委員會追究警方濫權<br />\n五、實行雙真普選</span></span>"},{"pid":"0bfb474da7763fe0c4701fe58ee76c50151b2905","tid":1304603,"uid":38761,"like":3,"dislike":11,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:53:58.000Z","msg":"點解無人推？<br />\n<br />\n地政咁得閒，大家比D野佢地做啦！"},{"pid":"4eea82f49db2f3315851c9435fd71beb40c9473c","tid":1304603,"uid":263161,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:58:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce19e6991928ef87fea8062e31ea47b71bbc2517","tid":1304603,"uid":29080,"like":71,"dislike":0,"score":71,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:00:35.000Z","msg":"清完咪又係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5e556f58c218010015e4cc6a6cf67322f0f63ee","tid":1304603,"uid":38761,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:02:12.000Z","msg":"有無其他大埔地政事宜需要跟進，請即聯絡大埔地政處<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tel.directory.